FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[Amount], [b0].[AuctionCarId], [b0].[BidType], [b0].[CreatedAt], [b0].[IPAddress], [b0].[IsAutoBid], [b0].[IsDeleted], [b0].[IsPreBid], [b0].[IsProxy], [b0].[Notes], [b0].[ParentBidId], [b0].[PlacedAtUtc], [b0].[ProcessedAt], [b0].[ProxyMax], [b0].[SequenceNumber], [b0].[Status], [b0].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b0].[UserAgent], [b0].[UserId], [b0].[ValidUntil]
    FROM [Bids] AS [b0]
    WHERE [b0].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionCarId]
WHERE [a].[AuctionId] = @__auctionId_0 AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Bids] AS [b]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId] AND [b].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY [a].[LotNumber], [a].[Id], [c].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ActiveStartTime], [t].[AuctionId], [t].[BidCount], [t].[CarId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[CurrentPrice], [t].[HammerPrice], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsReserveMet], [t].[ItemNumber], [t].[LastBidTime], [t].[LotNumber], [t].[MinPreBid], [t].[ReservePrice], [t].[SoldPrice], [t].[StartingPrice], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc], [t].[WinnerStatus], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[Id], [b].[Amount], [b].[AuctionCarId], [b].[BidType], [b].[CreatedAt], [b].[IPAddress], [b].[IsAutoBid], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[IsPreBid], [b].[IsProxy], [b].[Notes], [b].[ParentBidId], [b].[PlacedAtUtc], [b].[ProcessedAt], [b].[ProxyMax], [b].[SequenceNumber], [b].[Status], [b].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b].[UserAgent], [b].[UserId], [b].[ValidUntil], [t].[BodyStyle], [t].[Color], [t].[Condition], [t].[CreatedAt0], [t].[DriveTrain], [t].[EstimatedRetailValue], [t].[Fuel], [t].[HasKeys], [t].[IsDeleted0], [t].[LocationId], [t].[Make], [t].[Model], [t].[Odometer], [t].[OdometerUnit], [t].[OwnerId], [t].[PhotoUrls], [t].[PrimaryDamage], [t].[SecondaryDamage], [t].[TitleState], [t].[TitleType], [t].[Transmission], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc0], [t].[VideoUrls], [t].[Vin], [t].[Year], [t].[CreatedAt1], [t].[CreatedByUserId], [t].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [t].[CurrentCarStartTime], [t].[EndTimeUtc], [t].[ExtendedCount], [t].[IsDeleted1], [t].[IsLive], [t].[LocationId0], [t].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [t].[MinBidIncrement], [t].[Name], [t].[StartPrice], [t].[StartTimeUtc], [t].[Status], [t].[TimerSeconds], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[Amount], [b0].[AuctionCarId], [b0].[BidType], [b0].[CreatedAt], [b0].[IPAddress], [b0].[IsAutoBid], [b0].[IsDeleted], [b0].[IsPreBid], [b0].[IsProxy], [b0].[Notes], [b0].[ParentBidId], [b0].[PlacedAtUtc], [b0].[ProcessedAt], [b0].[ProxyMax], [b0].[SequenceNumber], [b0].[Status], [b0].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b0].[UserAgent], [b0].[UserId], [b0].[ValidUntil]
    FROM [Bids] AS [b0]
    WHERE [b0].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionCarId]
WHERE [a].[AuctionId] = @__auctionId_0 AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Bids] AS [b]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId] AND [b].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY [a].[LotNumber], [a].[Id], [c].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ActiveStartTime], [t].[AuctionId], [t].[BidCount], [t].[CarId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[CurrentPrice], [t].[HammerPrice], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsReserveMet], [t].[ItemNumber], [t].[LastBidTime], [t].[LotNumber], [t].[MinPreBid], [t].[ReservePrice], [t].[SoldPrice], [t].[StartingPrice], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc], [t].[WinnerStatus], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[Id], [b].[Amount], [b].[AuctionCarId], [b].[BidType], [b].[CreatedAt], [b].[IPAddress], [b].[IsAutoBid], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[IsPreBid], [b].[IsProxy], [b].[Notes], [b].[ParentBidId], [b].[PlacedAtUtc], [b].[ProcessedAt], [b].[ProxyMax], [b].[SequenceNumber], [b].[Status], [b].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b].[UserAgent], [b].[UserId], [b].[ValidUntil], [t].[BodyStyle], [t].[Color], [t].[Condition], [t].[CreatedAt0], [t].[DriveTrain], [t].[EstimatedRetailValue], [t].[Fuel], [t].[HasKeys], [t].[IsDeleted0], [t].[LocationId], [t].[Make], [t].[Model], [t].[Odometer], [t].[OdometerUnit], [t].[OwnerId], [t].[PhotoUrls], [t].[PrimaryDamage], [t].[SecondaryDamage], [t].[TitleState], [t].[TitleType], [t].[Transmission], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc0], [t].[VideoUrls], [t].[Vin], [t].[Year], [t].[CreatedAt1], [t].[CreatedByUserId], [t].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [t].[CurrentCarStartTime], [t].[EndTimeUtc], [t].[ExtendedCount], [t].[IsDeleted1], [t].[IsLive], [t].[LocationId0], [t].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [t].[MinBidIncrement], [t].[Name], [t].[StartPrice], [t].[StartTimeUtc], [t].[Status], [t].[TimerSeconds], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ActiveStartTime], [t].[AuctionId], [t].[BidCount], [t].[CarId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[CurrentPrice], [t].[HammerPrice], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsReserveMet], [t].[ItemNumber], [t].[LastBidTime], [t].[LotNumber], [t].[MinPreBid], [t].[ReservePrice], [t].[SoldPrice], [t].[StartingPrice], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc], [t].[WinnerStatus], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[Id], [b].[Amount], [b].[AuctionCarId], [b].[BidType], [b].[CreatedAt], [b].[IPAddress], [b].[IsAutoBid], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[IsPreBid], [b].[IsProxy], [b].[Notes], [b].[ParentBidId], [b].[PlacedAtUtc], [b].[ProcessedAt], [b].[ProxyMax], [b].[SequenceNumber], [b].[Status], [b].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b].[UserAgent], [b].[UserId], [b].[ValidUntil], [t].[BodyStyle], [t].[Color], [t].[Condition], [t].[CreatedAt0], [t].[DriveTrain], [t].[EstimatedRetailValue], [t].[Fuel], [t].[HasKeys], [t].[IsDeleted0], [t].[LocationId], [t].[Make], [t].[Model], [t].[Odometer], [t].[OdometerUnit], [t].[OwnerId], [t].[PhotoUrls], [t].[PrimaryDamage], [t].[SecondaryDamage], [t].[TitleState], [t].[TitleType], [t].[Transmission], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc0], [t].[VideoUrls], [t].[Vin], [t].[Year], [t].[CreatedAt1], [t].[CreatedByUserId], [t].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [t].[CurrentCarStartTime], [t].[EndTimeUtc], [t].[ExtendedCount], [t].[IsDeleted1], [t].[IsLive], [t].[LocationId0], [t].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [t].[MinBidIncrement], [t].[Name], [t].[StartPrice], [t].[StartTimeUtc], [t].[Status], [t].[TimerSeconds], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[Amount], [b0].[AuctionCarId], [b0].[BidType], [b0].[CreatedAt], [b0].[IPAddress], [b0].[IsAutoBid], [b0].[IsDeleted], [b0].[IsPreBid], [b0].[IsProxy], [b0].[Notes], [b0].[ParentBidId], [b0].[PlacedAtUtc], [b0].[ProcessedAt], [b0].[ProxyMax], [b0].[SequenceNumber], [b0].[Status], [b0].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b0].[UserAgent], [b0].[UserId], [b0].[ValidUntil]
    FROM [Bids] AS [b0]
    WHERE [b0].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionCarId]
WHERE [a].[AuctionId] = @__auctionId_0 AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Bids] AS [b]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId] AND [b].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY [a].[LotNumber], [a].[Id], [c].[Id]

    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[Amount], [b0].[AuctionCarId], [b0].[BidType], [b0].[CreatedAt], [b0].[IPAddress], [b0].[IsAutoBid], [b0].[IsDeleted], [b0].[IsPreBid], [b0].[IsProxy], [b0].[Notes], [b0].[ParentBidId], [b0].[PlacedAtUtc], [b0].[ProcessedAt], [b0].[ProxyMax], [b0].[SequenceNumber], [b0].[Status], [b0].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b0].[UserAgent], [b0].[UserId], [b0].[ValidUntil]

) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionCarId]

    FROM [Bids] AS [b]

) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionCarId]

FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[Amount], [b0].[AuctionCarId], [b0].[BidType], [b0].[CreatedAt], [b0].[IPAddress], [b0].[IsAutoBid], [b0].[IsDeleted], [b0].[IsPreBid], [b0].[IsProxy], [b0].[Notes], [b0].[ParentBidId], [b0].[PlacedAtUtc], [b0].[ProcessedAt], [b0].[ProxyMax], [b0].[SequenceNumber], [b0].[Status], [b0].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b0].[UserAgent], [b0].[UserId], [b0].[ValidUntil]
    FROM [Bids] AS [b0]
    WHERE [b0].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionCarId]
WHERE [a].[AuctionId] = @__auctionId_0 AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Bids] AS [b]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId] AND [b].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY [a].[LotNumber], [a].[Id], [c].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]

    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

2025-09-30 19:42:42.473 +04:00 [ERR] Failed executing DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__auctionId_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[AuctionCarId], [t].[BidType], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[IPAddress], [t].[IsAutoBid], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsPreBid], [t].[IsProxy], [t].[Notes], [t].[ParentBidId], [t].[PlacedAtUtc], [t].[ProcessedAt], [t].[ProxyMax], [t].[SequenceNumber], [t].[Status], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc], [t].[UserAgent], [t].[UserId], [t].[ValidUntil], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year]
FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[Amount], [b0].[AuctionCarId], [b0].[BidType], [b0].[CreatedAt], [b0].[IPAddress], [b0].[IsAutoBid], [b0].[IsDeleted], [b0].[IsPreBid], [b0].[IsProxy], [b0].[Notes], [b0].[ParentBidId], [b0].[PlacedAtUtc], [b0].[ProcessedAt], [b0].[ProxyMax], [b0].[SequenceNumber], [b0].[Status], [b0].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b0].[UserAgent], [b0].[UserId], [b0].[ValidUntil]
    FROM [Bids] AS [b0]
    WHERE [b0].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionCarId]
WHERE [a].[AuctionId] = @__auctionId_0 AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Bids] AS [b]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId] AND [b].[IsPreBid] = CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY [a].[LotNumber], [a].[Id], [c].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ActiveStartTime], [t].[AuctionId], [t].[BidCount], [t].[CarId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[CurrentPrice], [t].[HammerPrice], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsReserveMet], [t].[ItemNumber], [t].[LastBidTime], [t].[LotNumber], [t].[MinPreBid], [t].[ReservePrice], [t].[SoldPrice], [t].[StartingPrice], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc], [t].[WinnerStatus], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[Id], [b].[Amount], [b].[AuctionCarId], [b].[BidType], [b].[CreatedAt], [b].[IPAddress], [b].[IsAutoBid], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[IsPreBid], [b].[IsProxy], [b].[Notes], [b].[ParentBidId], [b].[PlacedAtUtc], [b].[ProcessedAt], [b].[ProxyMax], [b].[SequenceNumber], [b].[Status], [b].[UpdatedAtUtc], [b].[UserAgent], [b].[UserId], [b].[ValidUntil], [t].[BodyStyle], [t].[Color], [t].[Condition], [t].[CreatedAt0], [t].[DriveTrain], [t].[EstimatedRetailValue], [t].[Fuel], [t].[HasKeys], [t].[IsDeleted0], [t].[LocationId], [t].[Make], [t].[Model], [t].[Odometer], [t].[OdometerUnit], [t].[OwnerId], [t].[PhotoUrls], [t].[PrimaryDamage], [t].[SecondaryDamage], [t].[TitleState], [t].[TitleType], [t].[Transmission], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc0], [t].[VideoUrls], [t].[Vin], [t].[Year], [t].[CreatedAt1], [t].[CreatedByUserId], [t].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [t].[CurrentCarStartTime], [t].[EndTimeUtc], [t].[ExtendedCount], [t].[IsDeleted1], [t].[IsLive], [t].[LocationId0], [t].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [t].[MinBidIncrement], [t].[Name], [t].[StartPrice], [t].[StartTimeUtc], [t].[Status], [t].[TimerSeconds], [t].[UpdatedAtUtc1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]

) AS [t]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC

) AS [t]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[ActiveStartTime], [a].[AuctionId], [a].[BidCount], [a].[CarId], [a].[CreatedAt], [a].[CurrentPrice], [a].[HammerPrice], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsReserveMet], [a].[ItemNumber], [a].[LastBidTime], [a].[LotNumber], [a].[MinPreBid], [a].[ReservePrice], [a].[SoldPrice], [a].[StartingPrice], [a].[UpdatedAtUtc], [a].[WinnerStatus], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[Color], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c].[DriveTrain], [c].[EstimatedRetailValue], [c].[Fuel], [c].[HasKeys], [c].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [c].[LocationId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Odometer], [c].[OdometerUnit], [c].[OwnerId], [c].[PhotoUrls], [c].[PrimaryDamage], [c].[SecondaryDamage], [c].[TitleState], [c].[TitleType], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc0], [c].[VideoUrls], [c].[Vin], [c].[Year], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[CreatedByUserId], [a0].[CurrentCarLotNumber], [a0].[CurrentCarStartTime], [a0].[EndTimeUtc], [a0].[ExtendedCount], [a0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [a0].[IsLive], [a0].[LocationId] AS [LocationId0], [a0].[MaxCarDurationMinutes], [a0].[MinBidIncrement], [a0].[Name], [a0].[StartPrice], [a0].[StartTimeUtc], [a0].[Status], [a0].[TimerSeconds], [a0].[UpdatedAtUtc] AS [UpdatedAtUtc1]
    FROM [AuctionCars] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c] ON [a].[CarId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Auctions] AS [a0] ON [a].[AuctionId] = [a0].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[LotNumber] = @__lotNumber_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[Id] = [b].[AuctionCarId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [b].[PlacedAtUtc] DESC
